## Responsive Design
- Test on tablet sizes (common in farming operations)
- Ensure touch targets are adequately sized (44px minimum)
- Consider landscape orientation usage
- Account for outdoor visibility requirements

## Accessibility
- Use semantic HTML elements
- Provide alt text for field/crop images
- Ensure keyboard navigation works
- Use proper ARIA labels for farming-specific data